Package: PropCIsGUI
Type: Package
Title: Shiny Application for Confidence Intervals for Proportions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ralph", "Scherer",
    email = "shearer.ra76@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Ralph Scherer [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Ralph Scherer <shearer.ra76@gmail.com>
Description: A 'shiny' graphical interface exposing all confidence interval
    methods for proportions from the 'PropCIs' package. Supports single
    proportions (Wilson, Clopper-Pearson, mid-P, Blaker, Agresti-Coull),
    two independent proportions (difference, relative risk, odds ratio),
    matched pairs, and Bayesian credible intervals via Monte Carlo simulation.
    Only one method is computed at a time to prevent type I error inflation
    through cherry-picking of results.
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/shearer/PropCIsGUI
BugReports: https://github.com/shearer/PropCIsGUI/issues
Imports:
